<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<p class="p">The equation of the Levins hierarchical multispecies spatial competition model (
 <xref rid="R44" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">
  <italic class="italic">44</italic>
 </xref>) after the modifications of Hastings (
 <xref rid="R45" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">
  <italic class="italic">45</italic>
 </xref>) and Tilman (
 <xref rid="R46" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">
  <italic class="italic">46</italic>
 </xref>) is as follows
 <disp-formula class="disp-formula">
  <div id="m1" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
   <div class="mrow">
    <div class="mfrac">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">d</span>
      <div class="msub">
       <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
       <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">d</span>
      <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">t</span>
     </div>
    </div>
    <span class="mo">=</span>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">c</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <span stretchy="true" class="mo">(</span>
    <span class="mn">1</span>
    <span class="mo">−</span>
    <div displaystyle="true" class="mstyle">
     <div class="munderover">
      <span stretchy="true" class="mo">∑</span>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">j</span>
       <span class="mo">=</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
      <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">j</span>
    </div>
    <span stretchy="true" class="mo">)</span>
    <span class="mo">−</span>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">m</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <span class="mo">−</span>
    <span stretchy="true" class="mo">(</span>
    <div displaystyle="true" class="mstyle">
     <div class="munderover">
      <span stretchy="true" class="mo">∑</span>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">j</span>
       <span class="mo">=</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
       <span class="mo">−</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">c</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">j</span>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <span stretchy="true" class="mo">)</span>
    <span class="mo">−</span>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">s</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <div class="msub">
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">i</span>
    </div>
    <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">S</span>
   </div>
  </div>
 </disp-formula>where 
 <italic class="italic">p</italic>
 <sub xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <italic class="italic" xmlns="">i</italic>
 </sub> is the abundance of species 
 <italic class="italic">i</italic>, 
 <italic class="italic">c</italic>
 <sub xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <italic class="italic" xmlns="">i</italic>
 </sub> is the colonization efficiency of species 
 <italic class="italic">i</italic>, 
 <italic class="italic">m</italic>
 <sub xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <italic class="italic" xmlns="">i</italic>
 </sub> is the mortality rate of species 
 <italic class="italic">i</italic>, 
 <italic class="italic">s</italic>
 <sub xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <italic class="italic" xmlns="">i</italic>
 </sub> is the sensitivity to sedimentation of species 
 <italic class="italic">i</italic>, and 
 <italic class="italic">S</italic> is the sedimentation rate.
</p>
